From Michael Manning Subject Re Riceburner Respect In article Saint Craig writes Keeper of the 'Tude writes No anyone who is a true rider with the real riding attitude will offer a wave weather they are on a Harley or on a Honda or some other bike inless they have a serious case of my bike is better than your and you're too low to be This you'll find is the case with most of the harley riders out here where I am however I still give them a wave and ride secure in the knowlege that I'm a better persob than they perSOB I kinda like that Most people wave or return my wave when I'm on my Other Harley riders seldom wave back to me when I'm on my Squids don't wave or return waves ever even to each other from what I can Michael Manning NeXTMail FLSTF FatBoy Ducati